  "keyFeatures": [
    "On-chain Levenshtein distance scoring for continuous-gradient prediction markets",
    "Text prediction markets with 1,840 bits of information vs 1 bit for binary markets",
    "Complete market lifecycle: create, submit, resolve, claim payouts",
    "Genesis NFT system with fee revenue sharing",
    "Multi-wallet authentication (MetaMask + Coinbase Embedded Wallet)",
    "Decentralized oracle resolution for X.com posts",
    "AI-resistant market structure that deepens with AI capability improvements"
